  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other children were not so curious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But other children with me went later on, with me--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "-- with the roll wagon, and we went to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the one, sometimes it happens it was very cold, and we finished our job, you could go in only of course, in the compound when there was no transport.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our job was to take wood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was tremendous huge blocks of wood, which were used in the time of the Hungarian Jews, when the capacity of the four crematorium were not enough.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they built a new huge pit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this pit was done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In this way they put a lot of this wood, then benzene, and then the corpse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all this tremendous wood was laying in the crematorium, and around the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we brought the wood for normal heating in the autumn of Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if we loaded our roll wagon, everyone would sit and the kapo would say, children you can warm yourself in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because I knew all of it from before from the stories, I wanted to see everything, where is the special kind of place where it just was sliding old people and old cripples in the end of the end [NON-ENGLISH] around, which was where the people take off their clothes, was a shift from above down.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I imagine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, of course, they went also to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I saw the lift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lift of about a measurement 2 meters and 1 meter, which was only for the bodies, after the gassing, they took them out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with the lift, they put them up where really the ovens were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how well I know this people and crematorium there's a little story.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
